      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRESSING MATTERS (8) had been in super honest form hitting the frame four times on end before finishing fifth (19.86) at this track last time. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Goes well out of this box with a win and seven minor placings. Has ability and is a key runner. TWO GIRLS (3) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 6 lengths at this track in a handy 19.18 beating Buckle Up Miles. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Can measure up again. FOSSIL BLUFF (1) has mixed form recently, finishing sixth (16.75) in a Grade 3 at Launceston latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Can turn it around this time. SPIDER PIG (2) returns after a break and looks a top-three hope.",
